matter or something like that. Well, it could come up with new theories. Now, the question is,

00:17:01.940 --> 00:17:07.079
those theories still need to be proven because is it a new theory or is it a hallucination?

00:17:08.240 --> 00:17:14.680
Chances are. Hallucination. But I think there is something to be said for,

